#: sw_data.py:2437
msgid ""
"is the Wine console manager, used to run console commands and applications."
msgstr ""
"консольный менеджер Wine, используемый для запуска консольных команд и "
"приложений."

#: sw_data.py:2441
msgid ""
"is Wine's registry editor, similar in appearance and function to Window's "
